latestIgtvVideos.title: Mount Shasta Feb 2021
latestIgtvVideos.caption: Last week we took a beautiful short staycation to Mount Shasta! Here is a video montage of our complete trip summed up . The kiddos loved the snow, snow activities, sledding and the quality time we all got to spend together. We rented out an entire home in the woods and loved the experience. Now the kids love the sand and the snow equally😊 I am grateful that we could get this experience together as a family! #snowperfect #grateful #familytime #snowfamily #mountshasta #snowactivities #sledding #vdaycelebrations #myfamilyisthebest #love #reelitfeelit #travelblogger #videomontage #llivelifetothefullest #jdore #meghanmarkle #lovelife

latestIgtvVideos.title: Tahoe 2020
latestIgtvVideos.caption: Such an amazing and sweet short staycation we had at Tahoe. Thanks dear hubby to plan this amazing trip to celebrate our viv’s and my birthday! This is a video montage of our amazing amazing trip with the kiddos! There are so many more amazing pics and videos but can’t put them all so created a quick video😊 #familytrip2020 #tahoe #travelphotography #videomontage #familytime #myfamilyisthebest #blessed #besthubbyever #parentsoftwoboys #travelgram #lawofattraction #lovelife #savvipreneurs #savvidreamtribe #savvistyle #travel #Travelgram #traveling #Travelphotography #travelling #travelblogger #traveler
